Package courses

Class CourseElement

java.lang.Object
courses.CourseElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<CourseElement>
Direct Known Subclasses:
CalendarEvent, CourseAssignment, CourseDocument
public abstract class CourseElement
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<CourseElement>
This abstract class is used as a base class for the following objects: CourseAssignment CourseDocument CalendarEvent It is used as a parent class for storing the title of the element, the Date of the element and it's course name. This class is Immutable. It also implements the Comparable interface to allow sorting by date in the Course object's lists.
